Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:35.49,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(890,600)\be4}第23話 「隨風而逝的戰士」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}風…怎麼…被吸進瓦姆烏的管子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終流法——渾楔颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是風嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在火壇邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 我只能把握到你大概的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在你停止了波紋的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我橫掃過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能找到你的身體 切成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾楔颯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦姆烏的最終流法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同於讓身體透明的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這招是吸入大量的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肺內部極度壓縮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從窄如剃刀的縫隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以超高壓強噴射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說 是一道烈風之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 風的高速壓縮帶來的摩擦和熱力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是瓦姆烏的肉體也無法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會慢慢地受破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那凄慘的樣子 實在太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利是屬於你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏下這場戰鬥 用人類的生命治癒自己的傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想辦法反抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稱為 波紋油作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的體內 可以說是一個超濃縮的氧氣瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把這火焰瓶扔向他的管子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就會把火吸進去 引起體內爆炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這也是我的最終策略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失敗就要完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NWWW 找到了 在那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 吃招！瓦姆烏！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰瓶嗎 沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要離開火壇有一米距離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能感受到物體的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經束手無策了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你剛才的喊聲 讓我確定到你的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！渾楔颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西——撒——！靠你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要丟火種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你丟什麼 在我1米範圍內就能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我現在就把你切斷 就分出勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終…終於贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:14.58,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Ovunque tu vada
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:20.86,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Ovunque io vada
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:26.87,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}C'é il mio amor nella tua vita,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:34.30,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}c'é I'amor nella tua giornata
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:42.94,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Basta un tuo sorriso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:49.54,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}un tuo sol sorriso
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:58.08,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Non morirà I'alma mia. é immortal!
